item.title: [T_R] Full R.S.P.S Think Tank
item.dc:creator: @Teem_Rocket Teem_Rocket
item.description:
@Teem_Rocket wrote:

EDIT: I’ve given this user permission to release this via Skype. It’s just a small collaboration of ideas and brainstorming. I really do hope that at LEAST one person can get something out of this. Since this is a public release, everyone is free to re-post this on any and all websites. Although you may release it anywhere, I still request that myself and my ‘helpers’ be recognized.

-----Credits-----

Team_Rocket (Jack) - 90%.

Andrew_Speak (ox random xi) - 5%. Andrew gives great creative feedback and support. They were always ready to provide input on anything, no matter how silly or trivial it was, because he knew it was important.

Rune.Time (ThaKillah) - 5%. Rune.Time is another person who was asked to give feedback and provide input on original and unique content/features. Props to this guy for being patient and supporting T_R Developments.

I would also like to give additional credits to everyone on my Skype list who played a part in this. Although I was the only one writing this, a LOT of you were more than happy to offer me different perspectives and constructive criticism. I’d like to say thank you, and you all know who you are. COUGH LORENZO HADYN PULSER GAMMA COUGH

[b]P.S. I apologize for how messy and disorganized this is. I promise the new one, when It’s released, will have a MUCH better all-around format.
